                     <interp inst="t18000528-50-verdict281" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               Of stealing to the value of 39s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18000528-50-punish282" type="punishmentDescription">
